4
00:00:18,933 --> 00:00:21,026
放我走
Let me go.

5
00:00:29,877 --> 00:00:32,471
你想要我怎么样？
What do you want from me?

6
00:00:32,813 --> 00:00:34,713
说出真相
The truth.

7
00:00:39,713 --> 00:00:41,513
大都会，三年前
-Can I see some ID? -You must be new here.

8
00:00:40,688 --> 00:00:44,089
- 我能看看证件吗？ - 你是新来的吧

9
00:00:44,258 --> 00:00:46,726
没关系，让他进来
Hey, it's okay, let him through.

10
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:53,093
- 谢谢你，凯瑟 - 不客气
-Thanks, Kasich. -No problem.

11
00:00:56,804 --> 00:01:00,205
- 她很迷人 - 她订婚了
-She's cute. -She's engaged.

12
00:01:06,313 --> 00:01:08,338
觉得怎样？
What do you think?

13
00:01:12,786 --> 00:01:14,811
吵啊
It's loud.

14
00:01:16,190 --> 00:01:19,091
- 今晚有贵宾房间吗？ - 我想我们能准备一间给你
-How's the VIP room tonight? -I think we can make some room for you.

15
00:01:22,530 --> 00:01:24,794
我希望你不必觉得有义务让我开心
I hope you didn't feel obligated to entertain me.

16
00:01:24,965 --> 00:01:26,728
裘德只走了几天
Jude's only gone for a couple days.

17
00:01:26,901 --> 00:01:30,598
我不会觉得这是种义务 你未婚夫是帮了我
I don't believe in obligations. Besides, your fiance did me a favor.

18
00:01:30,771 --> 00:01:34,138
我也不想自己半夜出来玩
I wasn't looking forward to a night out on my own.

19
00:01:35,075 --> 00:01:38,772
直觉告诉我你应该才单身没太久
Something tells me you wouldn't have been alone for very long.

20
00:01:39,079 --> 00:01:42,048
- 两杯苹果马提尼酒 - 马上
-Two apple martinis. -Coming up.

21
00:01:44,451 --> 00:01:45,713
“零后果”
"Zero consequences."

22
00:01:46,620 --> 00:01:48,315
是个挺好的承诺
That's quite a promise.

23
00:01:48,489 --> 00:01:50,889
但要遵守才好
Only if it's kept.

24
00:01:51,192 --> 00:01:54,093
为了我好朋友阿曼达的订婚
To my good friend Amanda on her engagement.

25
00:01:54,261 --> 00:01:55,660
- 干杯 - 干杯
-Cheers. -Cheers.

26
00:01:59,500 --> 00:02:01,024
怎么了？
What is it?

27
00:02:02,970 --> 00:02:04,699
你在干什么？
What are you doing?

28
00:02:16,283 --> 00:02:19,081
- 阿曼达 - 你说你去出差了
-Amanda. -You said you had to go away on business.

29
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:21,488
听我解释，好吗？等等
I can explain, okay? Just wait.

30
00:02:21,722 --> 00:02:23,280
阿曼达，等下
Amanda, wait a sec--

31
00:02:24,925 --> 00:02:28,156
我可以解释，阿曼达，等等
I can explain, Amanda. Just wait. Amanda!

32
00:02:29,730 --> 00:02:32,995
杂种，你是故意带她来的
You son of a bitch. You did this on purpose.

33
00:02:33,801 --> 00:02:38,829
你自作自受，阿曼达该找个比你好的人
You did it to yourself. Amanda deserves better.

34
00:03:30,491 --> 00:03:35,121
骗子！笔录上是这么写的，但不是事实
Liar! That's what it said in the papers, but that's not what really happened.

35
00:03:35,296 --> 00:03:38,493
- 我说的是实话，看看警方笔录 - 我知道你隐瞒得很全面
-It's the truth. Read the police reports! -I know you covered it up.

36
00:03:38,666 --> 00:03:41,635
虽然我不知道你怎么做到的 但你会付出代价
I don't know how you did it, but you're gonna pay.

37
00:03:41,802 --> 00:03:43,394
你是谁？
Who are you?

38
00:03:44,505 --> 00:03:46,598
不记得了？
Don't you remember?

39
00:03:49,076 --> 00:03:50,475
你杀了我
You killed me.

40
00:03:58,652 --> 00:04:00,745
这次你爸也救不了你了，莱克斯
Daddy can't save you this time, Lex.

41
